## About

This is a decentralized blog, built on Solana. It was submitted during [IGNITION](https://ignition.devpost.com/) along with the [tutorial](https://github.com/DougAnderson444/solblog#solblog) and [video](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w-n87Aq3f8k) to help people learn what is possible, and how to code something familiar, on Solana.

[Watch the trailer](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k_cVwvXHO4U).

