## Blog Structure:

### Blogger Accounts (blogger)

Bloggers identities are any Ed25519 public keys, like the ones used in Solana. You can have as many blogger accounts as you like -- you just need to create a new public key. See the cheat code below about friendly name blogger accounts. 😉

### Blog Accounts (blogAccounts)

Blog accounts (or blog channels) are for a topic or an audience. Make as many channels as you want under the same Blogger, they are just new accounts in Solana under control of the Blogger's public key.

### Blog Links

Your blog is at:

`https://syncs.info/blog/YourBlogIdPublicKeyHere`

All your blogs listed at:

`https://syncs.info/blogger/YourBloggerPublicKeyHere`

List all your blogs using your Twitter handle, if [registered](https://naming.bonfida.org/#/twitter-registration):

`https://syncs.info/blogger/DougAnderson444`

